.
</emphasis>
The genus was re-established and described in detail by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bruce, N. L." box="[920,1065,154,178]" pageId="1" pageNumber="389" pagination="1 - 252" refId="ref2812" refString="Bruce, N. L. (2009) The marine fauna of New Zealand, Isopoda, Aegidae (Crustacea). NIWA Biodiversity Memoir, 122, 1 - 252." type="journal article" year="2009">Bruce (2009)</bibRefCitation>
